1. You receive a sales report where products are listed vertically by region, but your manager wants each region shown horizontally across columns. Without retyping, reorganize the data so that any update in the original table automatically updates the new one. (Hint: Use TRANSPOSE with dynamic references.)

2. A company tracks revenue and expenses per quarter. Use Goal Seek to determine the required sales in Q4 to achieve a total annual profit of $250,000, given fixed costs and tax rate.

